<div class="about-topic-content">
    <h3>
        Greenwich University Magazine - One of the UK's Top 10 Largest
        University Publications
    </h3>
    <p>
        Launched in 2023, Greenwich University Magazine provides students and
        faculty with a trusted and timely hub to access official information,
        campus happenings, and news from within the university community.
    </p>
    <p>
        Guided by the belief that seamless information flow is key to fostering
        engagement and connections across campus, we are committed to delivering
        captivating, diverse, and valuable content to all those invested in
        Greenwich University.
    </p>
    <br />
    <a class="findOutMoreButton" href="/">Find out more</a>
</div>
