    <div class="about-text-wrapper">
        <div class="about-text-item">
            <h5>Our Mission</h5>
            <p>
                Greenwich University Magazine aims to enrich our campus community by
                fostering connections and engagement through the power of open
                information sharing. We strive to create a platform that brings
                together students, faculty, staff, and alumni, promoting a vibrant
                exchange of ideas, stories, and perspectives that shape the
                Greenwich experience.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-text-item">
            <h5>Our Position</h5>
            <p>
                Through Greenwich University Magazine, members of the university
                community gain access to a comprehensive digital hub that connects
                them to a diverse array of stories, perspectives, and happenings
                across campus life. We facilitate a seamless experience for
                students, faculty, staff, and alumni to engage with the vibrant
                narratives that shape the Greenwich identity.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
